%vlocity_namespace%__Formula__c: QUERY("SELECT UserName FROM User WHERE Id = '{0}'", $Vlocity.UserId)
Name: valTransformAdjustmentsVoiceRequest

%vlocity_namespace%__Formula__c: IF(bucketSpecExternalId == "1", replaceString(TOSTRING(%NORImpugnValue%), ".", ","), IF(bucketSpecExternalId == "82", replaceString(TOSTRING(%SNSImpugnValue%), ".", ","), IF(bucketSpecExternalId == "136", replaceString(TOSTRING(%CACImpugnValue%), ".", ","), IF(bucketSpecExternalId == "138", replaceString(TOSTRING(%CAEImpugnValue%), ".", ","), ""))))
Name: valTransformAdjustmentsVoiceRequest

%vlocity_namespace%__Formula__c: QUERY("SELECT ChannelName__c FROM User WHERE Id = '{0}'", $Vlocity.UserId)
Name: valTransformAdjustmentsVoiceRequest

%vlocity_namespace%__Formula__c: IF(%service% == "Voice", "Impugnacao de Chamada de Voz", "Impugnacao Realizada pelo Operador")
Name: valTransformAdjustmentsVoiceRequest
